# Set specific line ending behavior for different file types
*.txt     text            # Normalize text files to LF line endings
*.md      text            # Normalize Markdown files to LF line endings
*.js      text eol=lf     # Force LF line endings for JavaScript files
*.css     text eol=crlf   # Force CRLF line endings for CSS files


# pattern1   option1
# pattern2   option2
# ...
# ```
# The `pattern` is a file name pattern like `*.txt` or `*.md`. The `option` is one of the following:
